At present, AI technology is developing at a high speed and has achieved remarkable results in the fields of voice, image, and natural language processing. Based on image and video fingerprint technology, we have built a smart cloud photo album platform, which aims to be a good helper for users to quickly and accurately find photoes.
Given main features of the album, we name the platform Remembrance that is intended to find memories. And the brand slogan is &ldquo;no hard to find memories.&rdquo;
We design the platform logo as a leaf. from the morphological point of view, it can also be understood as a pen made of feathers, which contains the meaning of &ldquo;recording&rdquo;. On the other hand, it is a bookmark made of leaves that helps the owner find the desired photoes in the album.

